{"tid":203088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯中途突然離隊捱轟","createTime":"2017-04-16T04:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T02:15:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e153ac6b8abf4f8f540b2534d6c304db7bc1f22","tid":203088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19991581&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19991581%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170416&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=dca3249d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19991581%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170416&h=796bd9ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19991581&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170416</a><br />\n<br />\n何君堯中途突然離隊捱轟<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n何君堯一度離團，並向已登車團員豎起拇指。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次立法會發展事務委員會到內地的考察雖短短兩天，團員之一的何君堯昨晨突然離隊，聲稱要自行外出用膳，有團員質疑他違反立法會內務守則的規定，不過其後何君堯歸隊繼續考察團行程，並隨同大隊返港。<br />\n<br />\n涉違內務守則規定<br />\n<br />\n考察團昨日行程是早上到東莞市參觀太園泵站，下午到深圳水庫等。不過昨晨大隊準備出發到東莞時，何君堯未有跟隨，從其他團員拍攝的影片所見，何一人未有登上旅遊巴，在酒店門口向其他已登車的團員揮手，並作出「吃飯」的手勢，當時其他議員議論紛紛，「約咗女朋友呀？」、「團長，出封警告信畀佢！」甚至有人提議向何展開「紀律聆訊」。<br />\n其後《蘋果》記者嘗試聯絡何了解離隊原因，但何未有解釋。據了解，一度離隊的何，最終在行程尾段歸隊繼續參與。不過根據立法會《內務守則》29A（b）的明文規定，無論委員會的委員或非委員，在參與外地訪問活動時應參與整個行程。<br />\n翻查資料顯示，過去亦發生過議員外訪期間中途離隊。2007年7月立法會民政事務委員會到澳門作一日考察期間，時為議員的霍震霆不單止自行乘船到澳門，更在考察團完成上午行程及用午膳後離隊返港，未有參與考察團下午的行程。<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n泛民建制下月辦跨黨飯局<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;6小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港記者被逐長毛不滿「維護兩地知情權應一視同仁」<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;6小時前"},{"pid":"139f8365a5f70114014e6609861bc48d0bf97eb4","tid":203088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170416/large/a0702a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170416%2Flarge%2Fa0702a.gif&h=706c3b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何君堯一度離團，並向已登車團員豎起拇指。"},{"pid":"685ba58c8843807f03cc261837af839f2937ec34","tid":203088,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"議員CALL G 唔洗你教"},{"pid":"44ec878b76a83d332ebfe37a257bf2d84f7e8bf5","tid":203088,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辣殺"},{"pid":"35fa034ea500ef403f08630e28c1b83b25948981","tid":203088,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56840aad4d4247e01e09f723708776d56ce82736","tid":203088,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"雞堯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f070f530a683c82f6406a411fbb1b8ad51310e","tid":203088,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"河妖:東芫囡囡一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4498a7270ab2b21ae917b6c5d9d475f46787df","tid":203088,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"何君堯：出糧出火發鳩痕"},{"pid":"3cde4cf4075e955981ddb25f54eff5a54175fda2","tid":203088,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"一早有G叫？"},{